name: Go Fetch! (itch)
description:
PLEASE PLAY IN FULLSCREEN!

Nekonyaa28 is close to debuting... Except, he kinda needs some funds to do so. He recently picked up a delivery job for the food delivery app Fetch™. Help him jump and slide to avoid obstacles in this endless runner to complete deliveries! You may run into some familiar faces along the way.

List of streamers featured (or planned) in the game in no particular order
  • Jae
  • ShimamoKaze
  • DannyDanchou
  • Ying
  • JelleeBun
  • Nekorichii
  • AyvuirRed
  • More to come!
This project wouldn't have been finished from the help of Parmpreet GillMusicRikoMusic Controls JumpSpace / Up ArrowSlideLeft Ctrl / Down Arrow Known Issues
  • Some people are having some issues trying to do multiple deliveries in a day. We've heard of some apps crashing. Just reload!
